definition: newly added/additional/to add (to what already exists)
abbr. for Xinjiang 新疆[Xin1 jiang1] or Singapore 新加坡[Xin1 jia1 po1]/surname Xin

sentences.english: We will increase our energy-saving capacity by an equivalent of 80 million tons of standard coal.
sentences.chinese: 今年要新增8000萬噸標準煤的節能能力。

sentences.english: Do you agree that most of the new seats in the 4th sector should be allocated to District Council members?
sentences.chinese: 是否贊成第四界別的新增議席，大部分分配給區議員？

sentences.english: In order to content the productive capacity of soda, a new calciner system was added.
sentences.chinese: 爲滿足純鹼生產能力，新增一套煅燒爐系統。

sentences.english: Brazilian clubs now have B teams and u 18 team. eg palmeiras.
sentences.chinese: 巴西俱樂部新增了B隊和18歲以下青年隊。

sentences.english: Added respawn time advantages when a team begins to cap any point.
sentences.chinese: 新增重生時間的優勢時，開始第一個團隊的任何一點。

sentences.english: The store is adding seven more staff in September who speak Chinese or English.
sentences.chinese: 該店將在9月新增七位會說中文或英語的員工。

sentences.english: Central finance has added 100 billion fund for agriculture.
sentences.chinese: 中央新增支農資金100億元。

sentences.english: The company added 16.8 million users between January and March, it said.
sentences.chinese: 消息稱，一至三月中國移動新增用戶有1680萬名。

sentences.english: The allocation of new education points is one of the typical problems in education planning.
sentences.chinese: 新增教學點的布點問題是教育規劃中典型問題之一。

sentences.english: Enhance your personal videos by adding professional looking fader effects.
sentences.chinese: 提高你的個人影片新增專業尋找推子影響。

sentences.english: Will a flood of new users dilute the quality of the Q&A site?
sentences.chinese: 大量的新增用戶是否會降低問答站點的質量？

sentences.english: New loans were a more-than-estimated 679.4 billion yuan ($104 billion) in March, it said.
sentences.chinese: 而且三月份的新增貸款6794億元，數字高於預期。

sentences.english: Historical battles, and lots of them, illustrating Alexanders major battles.
sentences.chinese: 新增諸多歷史戰役，囊括所有亞歷山大的主要會戰。

sentences.english: Staff at the Corado thought their new customers were attracted by the low prices.
sentences.chinese: 卡里多的工作人員認爲這些新增遊客是衝着低價而來。

sentences.english: A skill guide has been added to the Arena.
Add an exciting flavor to your day, with Trudeau.
sentences.chinese: 新增一個令人興奮的味道，你的一天，特魯多。
